# üìö Browse MCP

[English](README.md) | [‰∏≠Êñá](README_zh.md)

üî¨ `browse-mcp` is a Python-based MCP server that enables users to search, download, and read academic papers from various platforms. It provides three main tools:
- üîé **`paper_search`**: Search papers across multiple academic databases
- üì• **`paper_download`**: Download paper PDFs, return paths of downloaded files
- üìñ **`paper_read`**: Extract and read text content from papers

![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/browse-mcp.svg) ![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg) ![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.10+-blue.svg)

